      "summary": "The channel had minimal technical activity. The main substantive contribution was from shieldai, who introduced AgentAudit, a blockchain-based audit logging solution for AI agents designed for production ElizaOS deployments. The system provides immutable, tamper-proof logging of agent actions with EU AI Act compliance. It's currently deployed on Arbitrum Sepolia and Mantle Sepolia testnets at address 0x25ac2ab1369001F9C847e65f010B6e4f4340d78a. The TypeScript SDK is available, with a simple API that logs agent actions directly to the blockchain with metadata. An ElizaOS plugin integration is planned for release within the week. The implementation targets autonomous agents handling real transactions where auditability is critical. At the end of the segment, 0xnemian requested assistance with running a custom plugin but received no response during this timeframe. The rest of the chat consisted of brief exchanges about a scam message.",
